snippet.title: 77p egg: Eggwife - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
77p Studios is proud to reveal 77p egg: Eggwife! A dumb FPS  currently in development about love and sewage, inspired by classics such as Duke Nukem 3D and Postal 2, and new greats like DOOM and DUSK.

Follow development and shitpost with us on Discord: https://www.discord.io/77pStudios

Support the development of the game on Patreonnnnn:
https://www.patreon.com/77pstudios

Uhhhh, Twitter or something:
https://twitter.com/77pStudios
